Which option should be used to send a DNS query for an SPF record with dig?
A)  - t txt
B)  - t spf
C)  - t mx
D)  - t mailspf
A
A. SPF records are stored in the txt record type in DNS, thereby making - t txt thecorrect option for this. Of the other answers, only - t mx is valid and returns the mailexchangers for the given domain.
